<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[التنضيد]</span>: نَضَّد المتاعَ: إِذا ترك بعضه على بعض.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[التنضير]</span>: نَضَّر اللّاه وجهه: إِذا حَسَّنَه.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
